title: Derek Trucks- Songlines
description:
Songlines is the sixth album by American guitar phenomenon Derek Trucks and his group. The first studio album to feature his recently expanded sextet with vocalist Mike Mattison and percussionist Count M&#039;Butu joining Trucks (guitar and dobro), Todd Smallie (bass), Yonrico Scott (drums and percussion) and Kofi Burbridge (keyboards and flute).
